data.name: Ambrosia Apple and Cheese Platter
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and elegant platter featuring sweet Ambrosia apples paired with a variety of cheeses for a perfect snack or appetizer.
detailedCookingInstructions: Wash and slice the Ambrosia apples into wedges, leaving the skin on for added texture and flavor.
Arrange the apple slices on a large platter.
Cut the cheeses into bite-sized pieces or wedges and place them around the apples on the platter.
Drizzle honey over the apples and cheese for a touch of sweetness.
Sprinkle walnuts over the platter for added crunch.
Garnish with fresh mint leaves for a pop of color and freshness.
